title: Upper case sans serif font, slightly tall with an interesting W
content:
![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317131529im_/http:/typophile.com/files/jessfontcopy_3613.jpg)

This is all I have, it's a logo I didn't create. Possibly a free font as it wasn't done by an agency unless the person has access to fonts. Been through all the usual font identifiers, they couldn't quite match the W
